00:00:31.698 --> 00:00:34.501
120dB is way too easy

00:00:34.501 --> 00:00:35.168
With that said!

00:00:35.168 --> 00:00:38.805
Now, I want to use this app that measures volume

00:00:38.805 --> 00:00:42.142
Just how loud is... my noise level?

00:00:42.142 --> 00:00:42.580
So,

00:00:42.580 --> 00:00:43.730
for now,

00:00:43.730 --> 00:00:46.070
