00:00:47.247 --> 00:00:49.249
I think I’ve decided a theme!

00:00:49.249 --> 00:00:51.284
The first theme is:

00:00:51.284 --> 00:00:53.119
“What made me happy recently!”

00:00:53.653 --> 00:00:56.423
1.5 million subs!

00:00:56.423 --> 00:00:56.923
Oh!

00:00:57.120 --> 00:00:57.620
Huh?

00:00:58.291 --> 00:00:59.726
113...?

00:00:59.726 --> 00:01:01.728
Is this… broken?

00:01:01.728 --> 00:01:04.000
Wait, maybe this theme isn’t right

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:05.098
From a happy topic

00:01:05.098 --> 00:01:06.466
to an angry topic!

00:01:06.466 --> 00:01:07.700
Surely that would be more powerful!

00:01:07.700 --> 00:01:09.510
Let me try the challenge again, please!

00:01:09.510 --> 00:01:10.870
Well, next is:

00:01:10.870 --> 00:01:11.971
“The voice from my heart!”

00:01:12.530 --> 00:01:14.610
