00:01:15.508 --> 00:01:17.243
I’m out of ideas!

00:01:17.243 --> 00:01:19.679
119.5!

00:01:19.679 --> 00:01:21.314
About 120!

00:01:21.314 --> 00:01:22.916
SWEET!

00:01:22.916 --> 00:01:23.416
Ah...

00:01:25.919 --> 00:01:27.320
