00:01:27.320 --> 00:01:28.721
That was easy!

00:01:28.721 --> 00:01:29.250
Yep!

00:01:29.250 --> 00:01:30.824
That said, the result is:

00:01:30.824 --> 00:01:33.893
122.6dB!

00:01:33.893 --> 00:01:34.260
Well,

00:01:34.260 --> 00:01:35.361
that was too easy!

00:01:35.361 --> 00:01:35.940
Ah, y’know

00:01:35.940 --> 00:01:39.210
